import React from "react";
import KeypadRow from "./KeypadRow/KeypadRow";
import Button from "../../../components/Button/Button";

const keypad = () => (
    <section className="keypad">
      <KeypadRow>
        <Button />
        <Button />
        <Button />
        <Button />
      </KeypadRow>
      
      <KeypadRow>
        <Button />
        <Button />
        <Button />
        <Button />
      </KeypadRow>
      
      <KeypadRow>
        <Button />
        <Button />
        <Button />
        <Button />
      </KeypadRow>

      <KeypadRow>
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
    </KeypadRow>
    
    <KeypadRow>
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
      <Button />
    </KeypadRow>
  </section>
);

export default keypad;
